shared_text:
Elk Valley Lions Baseball
May 10, 2017 at 8:53 AM ·

Our game on Thursday is scheduled for 4:00 pm on the North Field vs. Udall.

Our State Playoff game is scheduled for 5:00 pm on Monday, May 15th, at Caney Valley vs. Caney Valley. We are the #5 seed.

Directions are to take US-75 through Caney. Go 2 blocks South of the Casey's on the right. You will turn West (right) on 6th Street. Once you cross the RR tracks, look for the Grain Elevators and the ball field should be just behind the elevators on the right.

Please keep Saturday, May 20th, open from 4-6pm, for our Baseball/Softball Backyard Blowout BBQ at the Fredonia Softball field. Families are asked to bring a side dish/dessert to share. Meats, buns, and condiments will be provided. Bring your glove, too!

Please bring a side dish/dessert to share, chairs upon which to sit, gloves with which to play, and a smile. Please email your RSVP (no OR yes AND number of folks - also, do you want Dogs, Burgers, or Don't Matter?!?) to Coach Russell (arussell@usd283.org) ...
